Summary: object noticed by my fiance traveled a long distant in short amount of time
divs: Sighting Detailsgray look disc-ish shaped object, high in the sky, clearly not a plane, not blinking lights, almost looked like a light shadow moving across the sky. traveled over our heads turned a little slowed down the left pretty fast. Traveled from one side of our visible sky to the other, a very long distance. There was a meteor shower going on, WAS not a meteor, ive seen a lot of meteors. I have a photo and a video but the video is so dark you cant see anything, it would need the light settings adjust.
